skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gainesville vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Gainesville. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Gainesville Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Gainesville Vegan for a fact."
